@startuml finding-state
!theme plain
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
  BorderColor #0277BD
}

[*] --> Draft : new finding
Draft --> Sent : notify owner
Sent --> InReview : owner accepts
InReview --> Accepted : approved
InReview --> Rejected : declined

Accepted --> Resolved : SRS updated
Rejected --> Closed : reason logged
Resolved --> [*]
Closed --> [*]

note bottom
  States ensure audit trail
  and change control
end note

@enduml